'''2015年珠穆朗玛峰雪崩事故'''发生在2015年4月25日，是[[矩震级|矩震级]]8.1级[[2015年尼泊尔地震|尼泊尔地震]]的次生灾害，地震波造成[[珠穆朗玛峰|珠穆朗玛峰]]山体晃动引发致命[[雪崩|雪崩]]，造成至少19人丧生，超过了[[2014年珠穆朗玛峰雪崩事故|一年多前的事故]]，成为了最致命的雪崩灾难。

== 雪崩 ==
地震发生时有数百人在珠穆朗玛峰<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/26/world/asia/nepal-earthquake-katmandu.html/|title=Earthquake Devastates Nepal, Killing More Than 1,900|publisher=NY Times|date=2015-04-26|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2015-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150426032626/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/26/world/asia/nepal-earthquake-katmandu.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。地震引发数次大雪崩，波及邻近山区。[[普莫里峰|普莫里峰]]附近出现的一次雪崩<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalgeographic.com/2015/04/150425-everest-earthquake-basecamp-nepal-himalaya-climbing-sherpa/|title=Everest Base Camp a ‘War Zone’ After Earthquake Triggers Avalanches|publisher=National Geographic|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428061313/http://news.nationalgeographic.com/2015/04/150425-everest-earthquake-basecamp-nepal-himalaya-climbing-sherpa/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，横扫[[昆布冰瀑|昆布冰瀑]]，席卷珠峰大本营<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2015/04/25/cfa47ee6-eb95-11e4-9a6a-c1ab95a0600b_story.html?hpid=z2|title=10 confirmed dead in Mount Everest avalanche, but toll expected to rise|date=2015-04-25|publisher=The Washington Post|accessdate=2015-04-26|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518114237/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2015/04/25/cfa47ee6-eb95-11e4-9a6a-c1ab95a0600b_story.html?hpid=z2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Sharma">{{cite news|author=Gopal Sharma|title=Seventeen bodies found at Everest base camp: Official|agency=Reuters|publisher=The Toronto Sun|url=http://www.torontosun.com/2015/04/25/seventeen-bodies-found-at-everest-base-camp-official|date=2015-04-25|accessdate=2015-04-30|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518091958/http://www.torontosun.com/2015/04/25/seventeen-bodies-found-at-everest-base-camp-official|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Graun>{{cite news|last1=Beaumont|first1=Peter|title=Deadly Everest avalanche triggered by Nepal earthquake|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/apr/25/deadly-everest-avalanche-triggered-by-nepal-earthquake|accessdate=2015-04-25|work=The Guardian|date=2015-04-25|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518081741/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/apr/25/deadly-everest-avalanche-triggered-by-nepal-earthquake|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2015/04/25/world/asia/nepal-earthquake-maps.html|title=Extent of the Damage From the Nepal Earthquake|publisher=NY Times|date=2015-04-26|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2015-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150426040441/http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2015/04/25/world/asia/nepal-earthquake-maps.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一名印度陆军登山队员从大本营南面寻获19具遗体，救出至少61人被困登山者<ref name="auto2">{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/04/25/asia/nepal-earthquake-everest|title='Huge disaster': Hikers around Everest run for lives, treat injured|work=CNN|accessdate=2015-04-30|archive-date=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428025538/http://edition.cnn.com/2015/04/25/asia/nepal-earthquake-everest|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto3">{{cite web|url=http://www.itv.com/news/update/2015-04-25/indian-army-18-bodies-found-on-everest-after-quake|title=Nepal earthquake: Over 1,900 dead as search for survivors continues|work=iTV.com|accessdate=2015-04-30|archive-date=2015-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150425155757/http://www.itv.com/news/update/2015-04-25/indian-army-18-bodies-found-on-everest-after-quake/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto4">{{cite web|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-indian-army-s-expedition-team-rescues-61-climbers-from-mount-everest-2080899|title=Indian Army's expedition team rescues 61 climbers from Mount Everest|work=DNA India|accessdate=2015-04-30|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402161019/https://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-indian-army-s-expedition-team-rescues-61-climbers-from-mount-everest-2080899|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

珠峰位于震中以东220千米处，有700人至1000多人被认为当时在山上，至少61人受伤，“数十人”失踪，更多人起初被困在高海拔的营地里，迷失了安全降落路线的方向。少数未被事故吓倒的登山者，力求尼泊尔政府允许他们重新攀登<ref name=Sharma/><ref name=Graun/><ref name=USAtoday1>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/04/26/mountaineers-guides-everest-avalanche/26410705|title=Mount Everest avalanche survivor: 'I had to survive'|date=2015-04-26|accessdate=2015-04-28|author=Gregory Korte and Aamer Madhani|work=USA Today|archive-date=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428152626/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/04/26/mountaineers-guides-everest-avalanche/26410705/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://news.yahoo.com/avalanche-sweeps-everest-nepal-30-injured-101133601.html "Avalanche sweeps Everest base camp, killing 17, injuring 61"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.yahoo.com/avalanche-sweeps-everest-nepal-30-injured-101133601.html |date=20150430061308 }}, 2015-04-25; 2015-04-28访问</ref><ref name=PostEverest>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/04/25/massive-avalanche-slams-into-everest-base-camp-following-nepal-earthquake|title=Massive avalanche slams into Everest base camp following Nepal earthquake|date=2015-04-25|accessdate=2015-04-28|author=Peter Holley|work=Washington Post|archive-date=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428080017/http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/04/25/massive-avalanche-slams-into-everest-base-camp-following-nepal-earthquake/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=USATodayEverest>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/04/25/mount-everest-climbers-mazur/26355255|title=At least 10 dead, others missing as Nepal quake rocks Mount Everest|date=2015-04-25|accessdate=2015-04-28|author=Melanie Eversley and Tom Vanden Brook|work=USA Today|archive-date=2015-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150427211423/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/04/25/mount-everest-climbers-mazur/26355255/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 搜救 ==
印度空军直升机4月26日上午抵达珠穆朗玛峰展开救援行动<ref name="auto5">{{cite web|url=http://www.firstpost.com/india/live-first-rescue-plane-lands-at-kathmandu-airport-with-15-injured-from-mt-everest-avalanche-2212618.html|title=Live: First rescue plane lands at Kathmandu airport with 15 injured from Mt. Everest avalanche|work=firstpost.com|accessdate=2015-04-30|archive-date=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428161616/http://www.firstpost.com/india/live-first-rescue-plane-lands-at-kathmandu-airport-with-15-injured-from-mt-everest-avalanche-2212618.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，将22名重伤者送往裴丽切村（{{lang|en|Pheriche}}），但行动因天气恶劣而被叫停<ref name=NYTAvalanche>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/26/world/asia/everest-climbers-killed-as-nepal-quake-sets-off-avalanche.html|date=2015-04-25|accessdate=2015-04-28|author=Gardiner Harris|work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|title=At Least 10 Everest Climbers Killed as Nepal Quake Sets Off Avalanche|archive-date=2015-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150426033836/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/26/world/asia/everest-climbers-killed-as-nepal-quake-sets-off-avalanche.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。裴丽切是登山者的重要中转站，外国志愿者和当地人在当地设置了一所简陋的医院。

当天晚些时候，一架直升机据称从珠峰一号大本营撤出数名登山者，大本营上方的第一阶梯仍有100人无法安全降至一号和二号营地<ref name=ReutersEvacuation>{{cite news|author=Sanjeev Miglani|date=2015-04-26|accessdate=2015-04-28|url=http://news.yahoo.com/seventeen-bodies-recovered-worst-everest-disaster-030022373.html|title=Injured flown from Everest, aftershock triggers new avalanches|work=Reuters|archive-date=2015-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150503083942/http://news.yahoo.com/seventeen-bodies-recovered-worst-everest-disaster-030022373.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。更多人于4月27日获救<ref>{{cite web|last1=Zoroya|first1=Gregg|title=High-altitude helicopter rescues begin on Mt. Everest|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/04/27/earthquake-everest-climbers-avalanche-trapped/26445519|website=USA Today|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2015-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150429200041/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/04/27/earthquake-everest-climbers-avalanche-trapped/26445519/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。处在大本营的登山者在灾难发生几天后发布[[Twitter|Twitter]]称留下来的人“悲凉得伟大”，“高度尚未确定”。灾区看上去好像被核弹击中。一名登山者透过[[Facebook|Facebook]]表示，被困于高处的人们“越来越绝望”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/climbers-trapped-on-mount-everest-are-getting-desperate/2015/04/26/68ec0765-9303-4aec-b7ec-f031cdae42fc_story.html?tid=pm_pop|title=Climbers trapped on Mount Everest 'are getting desperate'|work=Washington Post|accessdate=2015-04-27|archive-date=2015-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150427145342/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/climbers-trapped-on-mount-everest-are-getting-desperate/2015/04/26/68ec0765-9303-4aec-b7ec-f031cdae42fc_story.html?tid=pm_pop|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月27日有60人从一号营地救出，170人从二号营地救出<ref name="NMA">[http://www.nepalmountaineering.org/newspage-223-Update%20News%20about%20avalanche%20at%20Everest Update News about avalanche at Everest] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nepalmountaineering.org/newspage-223-Update%20News%20about%20avalanche%20at%20Everest |date=20150518080736 }}, Nepal Mountaineering Association, 28 April, 2015</ref>。

4月25日发现17具尸体，4月27日又发现一具。4月26日，61名重伤者中的一名在KMC医院去世<ref name="NMA" />。

== 死者 ==
[[Google|Google]]員工[[丹·福瑞迪博格|丹·福瑞迪博格]]（{{lang|en|Dan Fredinburg}}）与公司另外三名员工攀登珠峰，为[[Google地球|Google地球]]类项目测绘时遭遇雪崩身亡<ref name=NYTFredinburg>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/26/business/google-adventurer-dies-on-mt-everest.html|date=2015-04-25|accessdate=2015-04-28|title='Google Adventurer' Dies on Mt. Everest|work=New York Times|author=Conor Dougherty|archive-date=2015-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150426034421/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/26/business/google-adventurer-dies-on-mt-everest.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=DailyMail>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3057525/If-don-t-return-ll-know-ve-lived-equivalent-100-lives-heartbreaking-letter-friend-Google-engineer-carrying-read-Everest-summit-avalanche-killed-him.html|title='If you don't return we'll know that you've already lived the equivalent of at least 100 lives': The heartbreaking letter from a friend Google engineer was carrying to read at Everest summit before avalanche killed him|date=2015-04-27|accessdate=2015-04-27|work=Daily Mail|author=Wills Robinson|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518100800/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3057525/If-don-t-return-ll-know-ve-lived-equivalent-100-lives-heartbreaking-letter-friend-Google-engineer-carrying-read-Everest-summit-avalanche-killed-him.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=WPost>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/04/28/four-americans-killed-in-everest-avalanche-were-exactly-where-they-wanted-to-be/|title=Before the Everest avalanche, four Americans were exactly where they wanted to be|work=Washington Post|author=Peter Holley|date=2015-04-28|accessdate=2015-04-29|archive-date=2015-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150504225156/http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/04/28/four-americans-killed-in-everest-avalanche-were-exactly-where-they-wanted-to-be/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

4月28日尼泊尔登山协会公布19名死者名单，其中10名为尼泊尔[[夏尔巴人|夏尔巴人]]，5名外国登山者，有4人身份尚未确认<ref>[http://www.nepalmountaineering.org/newspage-225-Name%20List%20of%2015%20identified%20dead%20body%20among%2019%20dead%20body%20found%20at%20Mt.%20Everest Name List of 15 identified dead body among 19 dead body found at Mt. Everest] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nepalmountaineering.org/newspage-225-Name%20List%20of%2015%20identified%20dead%20body%20among%2019%20dead%20body%20found%20at%20Mt.%20Everest |date=20150505100836 }}, Nepal Mountaineering Association, April 28, 2015</ref>。5名外国登山者中有2名美国人，1名中国人，1名澳大利亚人，1名日本人<ref>[http://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2015/04/29/the-latest-on-nepal-under-rubble-man-says-he-drank-urine The Latest on Nepal: In Ravaged Hamlets, Lives Were Spared] {{Wayback|url=http://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2015/04/29/the-latest-on-nepal-under-rubble-man-says-he-drank-urine |date=20150504203827 }}, ''U.S. News and World Reports'', April 29, 2015</ref>。

== 影响 ==
昆布冰瀑阶梯在事故中损坏<ref name=IndianExpress>{{cite news|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/india/india-others/undeterred-by-quake-assam-mountaineers-wait-in-base-camp-for-nepal-govt-decision/|title=Assam mountaineers undetterred after avalanche await Nepal govt’s permission to climb Everest|work=The Indian Express|date=2015-04-28|accessdate=2015-04-29|author=Samudra Gupta Kashyap|archive-date=2015-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150505100859/http://indianexpress.com/article/india/india-others/undeterred-by-quake-assam-mountaineers-wait-in-base-camp-for-nepal-govt-decision/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而申请再次攀登的登山者于2015年4月29日获准<ref name=PermitsGrantedAFP>{{cite news|url=http://news.yahoo.com/climbing-resume-mount-everest-next-week-official-052906487.html|title=Climbing to resume on Mount Everest by next week: official|date=2015-04-29|accessdate=2015-04-30|work=Agence France-Presse|archive-date=2015-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150503090519/http://news.yahoo.com/climbing-resume-mount-everest-next-week-official-052906487.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。“梯子将在未来两到三天内修复，攀登会继续下去，任何人都没有理由去放弃他们的远征，”尼泊尔旅游部负责任图尔西·高塔姆表示：“尽管没有预测另一场地震的科学依据......但我们认为地面适合攀登，尽管余震不够稳定。”<ref name=PermitsGrantedAFP/>

